Autorenfoto BUNT Blau" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></picture></div></header></div><div class="c-teaser__container is-full-height-flex"><div class="c-teaser__overline"><div class="c-teaser__ellipsis-container"><span class="c-teaser__badge is-premium" data-external="Teaser.PremiumIcon"><svg class="c-teaser__premium-icon u-icon is-logo-welt-plus-small"><title>Weltplus Artikel</title><use href="#logo-welt-plus-small"></use></svg></span><span class="c-teaser__topic" data-external="Teaser.Topic">Bundeswehr</span></div></div><div class="c-teaser__body" data-external="Teaser.Body"><h4 class="c-teaser__headline" data-external="Teaser.Title"><a class="is-link c-teaser__headline-link is-teaser-link is-emphasis" href="/debatte/plus68ecc34cff70575ab37a2233/bundeswehr-wehrpflicht-per-los-der-plan-der-regierung-ist-verlogen-und-ungerecht.html" title="Herzlichen Glückwunsch, Sie werden eingezogen!" data-external="Teaser.Link" data-internal-tracking-enabled="true" data-internal-tracking="{&quot;action&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;news_a_plus&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Inline Element&quot;,&quot;data&quot;:{&quot;source&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;/debatte/plus68ecc34cff70575ab37a2233/bundeswehr-wehrpflicht-per-los-der-plan-der-regierung-ist-verlogen-und-ungerecht.html&quot;,&quot;trackingName&quot;:&quot;Herzlichen Glückwunsch, Sie werden eingezogen!&quot;,&quot;trackingLabel&quot;:&quot;Herzlichen Glückwunsch, Sie werden eingezogen!&quot;}}" aria-label="Weltplus Artikel - Bundeswehr: Herzlichen Glückwunsch, Sie werden eingezogen!">Herzlichen Glückwunsch, Sie werden eingezogen!</a></h4><p class="c-teaser__intro" data-external="Teaser.Intro">Per Lotterie an die Front? Genau das droht jungen deutschen Männern nach Plänen der Bundesregierung im Extremfall. Doch der Staat darf nicht Schicksal spielen.</p></div><script type="application/hydration-data" data-internal-ref="TeaserFooter-c578bea8-cd87-4577-7822-a3d0dde2d9d3">{"teaserId":"68ecc34cff70575ab37a2233","showCommentCount":true,"author":{"name":"Andreas Rosenfelder"}}</script><div data-component="TeaserFooter" data-internal-id="TeaserFooter-c578bea8-cd87-4577-7822-a3d0dde2d9d3" class="is-teaser-footer-hydrated"><footer class="c-teaser__footer" data-external="Teaser.Footer"><ul class="c-teaser__footer-list"><li class="c-teaser__footer-list-item"><span class="c-teaser__author" data-external="Teaser.Author">Andreas Rosenfelder</span></li></ul></footer></div></div></article></div><div data-external="Stage.Item" class="u-grid-item is-grid-col-mobile-s-12 is-grid-col-mobile-l-6 is-grid-col-tablet-l-4"><article class="c-teaser c-teaser--default" data-external="Teaser" data-external-id="68e7711aa17cb4f03352aa64"><div class="c-teaser__container"><header class="c-teaser__header" data-external="Teaser.Header"><div class="c-picture has-placeholder-image is-aspect-ratio-mobile-s-23x11  c-picture--default" data-external="Teaser.PictureElement.Placeholder"><picture class="c-picture__image-container is-aspect-ratio-mobile-s-23x11 "><source media="(min-width:0px)" srcSet="https://images.welt.de/68e7711aa17cb4f03352aa64/500d0d04e571493de97e1426983ec776/ci23x11-w200/russian-president-putin-participates-in-commonwealth-of-independent-states-summit-in-tajikistan 200w, https://images.welt.de/68e7711aa17cb4f03352aa64/500d0d04e571493de97e1426983ec776/ci23x11-w400/russian-president-putin-participates-in-commonwealth-of-independent-states-summit-in-tajikistan 400w, https://images.welt.de/68e7711aa17cb4f03352aa64/500d0d04e571493de97e1426983ec776/ci23x11-w600/russian-president-putin-participates-in-commonwealth-of-independent-states-summit-in-tajikistan 600w, https://images.welt.de/68e7711aa17cb4f03352aa64/500d0d04e571493de97e1426983ec776/ci23x11-w800/russian-president-putin-participates-in-commonwealth-of-independent-states-summit-in-tajikistan 800w, https://images.welt.de/68e7711aa17cb4f03352aa64/500d0d04e571493de97e1426983ec776/ci23x11-w1000/russian-president-putin-participate