ldorf, 04.10.2024," loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></picture></div></header></div><div class="c-teaser__container is-full-height-flex"><div class="c-teaser__overline"><div class="c-teaser__ellipsis-container"><span class="c-teaser__badge is-premium" data-external="Teaser.PremiumIcon"><svg class="c-teaser__premium-icon u-icon is-logo-welt-plus-small"><title>Weltplus Artikel</title><use href="#logo-welt-plus-small"></use></svg></span><span class="c-teaser__topic" data-external="Teaser.Topic">Bundeswehr</span></div></div><div class="c-teaser__body" data-external="Teaser.Body"><h4 class="c-teaser__headline" data-external="Teaser.Title"><a class="is-link c-teaser__headline-link is-teaser-link" href="/politik/deutschland/plus68e8b5450bda2290ccea68b7/bundeswehr-aufmacher-plus-oh-die-grosse-wehrdienst-lotterie.html" title="Die große Wehrdienst-Lotterie" data-external="Teaser.Link" data-internal-tracking-enabled="true" data-internal-tracking="{&quot;action&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;welt-plus_a_plus&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Inline Element&quot;,&quot;data&quot;:{&quot;source&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;/politik/deutschland/plus68e8b5450bda2290ccea68b7/bundeswehr-aufmacher-plus-oh-die-grosse-wehrdienst-lotterie.html&quot;,&quot;trackingName&quot;:&quot;Die große Wehrdienst-Lotterie&quot;,&quot;trackingLabel&quot;:&quot;Die große Wehrdienst-Lotterie&quot;}}" aria-label="Weltplus Artikel - Bundeswehr: Die große Wehrdienst-Lotterie">Die große Wehrdienst-Lotterie</a></h4><p class="c-teaser__intro" data-external="Teaser.Intro">In der Debatte um die Gestaltung des künftigen Wehrdiensts wird nun über ein Losverfahren gesprochen. Verteidigungsminister Pistorius ließ sich mehr vom SPD-Parteitag als von militärischer Logik leiten – und nutzte teils fragwürdige Zahlen. Eine zentrale Frage bleibt weiterhin unbeantwortet.</p></div><script type="application/hydration-data" data-internal-ref="TeaserFooter-7efc12ee-214f-4974-8383-f16f48add83f">{"teaserId":"68e8b5450bda2290ccea68b7","showCommentCount":true,"author":{"name":"Thorsten Jungholt"}}</script><div data-component="TeaserFooter" data-internal-id="TeaserFooter-7efc12ee-214f-4974-8383-f16f48add83f" class="is-teaser-footer-hydrated"><footer class="c-teaser__footer" data-external="Teaser.Footer"><ul class="c-teaser__footer-list"><li class="c-teaser__footer-list-item"><span class="c-teaser__author" data-external="Teaser.Author">Thorsten Jungholt</span></li></ul></footer></div></div></article></div><div data-external="Stage.Item" class="u-grid-item is-grid-col-mobile-s-12 is-grid-col-mobile-l-6 is-grid-col-tablet-l-4"><article class="c-teaser c-teaser--default" data-external="Teaser" data-external-id="68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3"><div class="c-teaser__container"><header class="c-teaser__header" data-external="Teaser.Header"><div class="c-picture has-placeholder-image is-aspect-ratio-mobile-s-23x11  c-picture--default" data-external="Teaser.PictureElement.Placeholder"><picture class="c-picture__image-container is-aspect-ratio-mobile-s-23x11 "><source media="(min-width:0px)" srcSet="https://images.welt.de/68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3/e5060482b79af615433a16db1ca55c55-master/ci23x11-w200/lower-manhattan-and-the-financial-district-at-sunset-new-york-city-with-clouds 200w, https://images.welt.de/68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3/e5060482b79af615433a16db1ca55c55-master/ci23x11-w400/lower-manhattan-and-the-financial-district-at-sunset-new-york-city-with-clouds 400w, https://images.welt.de/68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3/e5060482b79af615433a16db1ca55c55-master/ci23x11-w600/lower-manhattan-and-the-financial-district-at-sunset-new-york-city-with-clouds 600w, https://images.welt.de/68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3/e5060482b79af615433a16db1ca55c55-master/ci23x11-w800/lower-manhattan-and-the-financial-district-at-sunset-new-york-city-with-clouds 800w, https://images.welt.de/68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3/e5060482b79af615433a16db1ca55c55-master/ci23x11-w1000/lower-manhattan-and-the-financial-district-at-sunset-new-york-city-with-clouds 1000w, https://images.welt.de/68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3/e5060482b79af615433a16db1ca55c55-master/ci23x11-w1200/lower-manhattan-and-the-financial-district-at-sunset-new-york-city-with-clouds 1200w, https://images.welt.de/68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3/e5060482b79af615433a16db1ca55c55-master/ci23x11-w1400/lower-manhattan-and-the-financial-district-at-sunset-new-york-city-with-clouds 1400w, https://images.welt.de/68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3/e5060482b79af615433a16db1ca55c55-master/ci23x11-w1600/lower-manhattan-and-the-financial-district-at-sunset-new-york-city-with-clouds 1600w, https://images.welt.de/68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3/e5060482b79af615433a16db1ca55c55-master/ci23x11-w1800/lower-manhattan-and-the-financial-district-at-sunset-new-york-city-with-clouds 1800w, https://images.welt.de/68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3/e5060482b79af615433a16db1ca55c55-master/ci23x11-w2000/lower-manhattan-and-the-financial-district-at-sunset-new-york-city-with-clouds 2000w" sizes="(min-width: 910px) calc(970px / 3), (min-width: 600px) 50vw, 100vw"/><img src="https://images.welt.de/68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3/e5060482b79af615433a16db1ca55c55-master/ci23x11-w200/lower-manhattan-and-the-financial-district-at-sunset-new-york-city-with-clouds" class="c-picture__image" alt="View of Lower Manhattan, the financial district and One World Trade Centre with clouds at sunset. New York City" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></picture></div></header></div><div class="c-teaser__container is-full-height-flex"><div class="c-teaser__overline"><div class="c-teaser__ellipsis-container"><span class="c-teaser__badge is-premium" data-external="Teaser.PremiumIcon"><svg class="c-teaser__premium-icon u-icon is-logo-welt-plus-small"><title>Weltplus Artikel</title><use href="#logo-welt-plus-small"></use></svg></span><span class="c-teaser__topic" data-external="Teaser.Topic">McKinsey-Studie</span></div></div><div class="c-teaser__body" data-external="Teaser.Body"><h4 class="c-teaser__headline" data-external="Teaser.Title"><a class="is-link c-teaser__headline-link is-teaser-link" href="/wirtschaft/plus68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3/mckinsey-studie-die-wahrheit-ueber-den-unfassbaren-reichtum-der-welt.html" title="Die Wahrheit über den unfassbaren Reichtum der Welt" data-external="Teaser.Link" data-internal-tracking-enabled="true" data-internal-tracking="{&quot;action&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;welt-plus_a_plus&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Inline Element&quot;,&quot;data&quot;:{&quot;source&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;/wirtschaft/plus68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3/mckinsey-studie-die-wahrheit-ueber-den-unfassbaren-reichtum-der-welt.html&quot;,&quot;trackingName&quot;:&quot;Die Wahrheit über den unfassbaren Reichtum der Welt&quot;,&quot;trackingLabel&quot;:&quot;Die Wahrheit über den unfassbaren Reichtum der Welt&quot;}}" aria-label="Weltplus Artikel - McKinsey-Studie: Die Wahrheit über den unfassbaren Reichtum der Welt">Die Wahrheit über den unfassbaren Reichtum der Welt</a></h4><p class="c-teaser__intro" data-external="Teaser.Intro">Ein McKinsey-Report beziffert den Wohlstand der Welt auf eine unvorstellbare Summe. Viel von dem in den vergangenen Jahrzehnten geschaffenem Reichtum existiert jedoch nur „auf dem Papier“. Wer jetzt Risiken und Hoffnungen kennt, kann sich bei der Geldanlage richtig positionieren.</p></div><script type="application/hydration-data" data-internal-ref="TeaserFooter-1a41a388-1141-4228-819f-cc59e6abc322">{"teaserId":"68e8d0e5675f132d327b49e3","showCommentCount":true,"author":{"name":"Daniel Eckert"}}</script><div data-component="TeaserFooter" data-internal-id="TeaserFooter-1a41a388-1141-4228-819f-cc59e6abc322" class="is-teaser-footer-hydrated"><footer class="c-teaser__footer" data-external="Teaser.Footer"><ul class="c-teaser__footer-list"><li class="c-teaser__footer-list-item"><span class="c-teaser__author" data-external="Teaser.Author">Daniel Eckert</span></li></ul></footer></div></div></article></div><div data-external="Stage