weg, Jobs in Gefahr: Hamburg hat mit geringer Wahlbeteiligung für schärfere Klimaschutzmaßnahmen gestimmt. Gravierende Einschnitte sind nun verpflichtend, doch dem Klimaschutz dürfte der Entscheid einen Bärendienst erweisen.</p></div><script type="application/hydration-data" data-internal-ref="TeaserFooter-cbb4931f-f57d-4cc1-76c8-50ec11c64d09">{"teaserId":"68ec2bc8ff70575ab37a1b70","showCommentCount":true,"author":{"name":"Axel Bojanowski"}}</script><div data-component="TeaserFooter" data-internal-id="TeaserFooter-cbb4931f-f57d-4cc1-76c8-50ec11c64d09" class="is-teaser-footer-hydrated"><footer class="c-teaser__footer" data-external="Teaser.Footer"><ul class="c-teaser__footer-list"><li class="c-teaser__footer-list-item"><span class="c-teaser__author" data-external="Teaser.Author">Axel Bojanowski</span></li></ul></footer></div></div></article></div></div></section><hr class="c-divider c-divider--stage"/><section class="c-tag-cloud-compact-stage is-content-visibility-auto c-tag-cloud-compact-stage--default is-theme-welt-blue" data-external-stage-name="tag-cloud-compact"><header class="c-tag-cloud-compact-stage__header"><a class="is-link c-tag-cloud-hero-stage__headline-link" href="/meinewelt/newsletter" title="Unsere Newsletter" data-internal-tracking-enabled="true" data-internal-tracking="{&quot;action&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;link&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Inline Element&quot;,&quot;data&quot;:{&quot;source&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;/meinewelt/newsletter&quot;,&quot;trackingName&quot;:&quot;Unsere Newsletter&quot;,&quot;trackingLabel&quot;:&quot;Unsere Newsletter&quot;}}"><h4 class="c-tag-cloud-compact-stage__headline">Unsere Newsletter</h4></a></header><div class="c-tag-cloud-compact-stage__body"><div class="c-tag-cloud-compact-stage__list-wrapper"><ul class="c-tag-cloud-compact-stage__list"><li class="c-tag-cloud-compact-stage__list-item"><div class="c-chip is-theme-welt-blue c-chip--tag-cloud-stage"><a class="is-link c-ch