ylian-mbappe-in-real-madrid 2000w" sizes="(min-width: 910px) calc(970px / 3), (min-width: 600px) 50vw, 100vw"/><img src="https://images.welt.de/68ece65a5e77548821fa1d0d/ef3415f6260a369f9a8606e160e13379/ci23x11-w200/football-presentation-kylian-mbappe-in-real-madrid" class="c-picture__image" alt="Wilfrid (Wilfried) MBAPPE father of Kylian MBAPPE, Fayza LAMARI mother of Kylian MBAPPE and Kylian MBAPPE during his presentation as a new player of Real Madrid CF on 16 July 2024 at Santiago Bernabeu stadium in Madrid, Spain - Photo Matthieu Mirville / DPPI" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></picture></div></header></div><div class="c-teaser__container is-full-height-flex"><div class="c-teaser__overline"><div class="c-teaser__ellipsis-container"><span class="c-teaser__badge " data-external="Teaser.Badge"><a class="is-link c-teaser__badge-link is-teaser-link" href="/sport/fussball/internationale-ligen/" title="Internationale Ligen" data-internal-tracking-enabled="true" data-internal-tracking="{&quot;action&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;link&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Inline Element&quot;,&quot;data&quot;:{&quot;source&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;/sport/fussball/internationale-ligen/&quot;,&quot;trackingName&quot;:&quot;Internationale Ligen&quot;,&quot;trackingLabel&quot;:&quot;Internationale Ligen&quot;}}" tabindex="-1"><span class="u-visually-hidden">Ressort<!-- -->:</span>Internationale Ligen</a></span><span class="c-teaser__topic" data-external="Teaser.Topic">Mbappés Mutter</span></div></div><div class="c-teaser__body" data-external="Teaser.Body"><h4 class="c-teaser__headline" data-external="Teaser.Title"><a class="is-link c-teaser__headline-link is-teaser-link" href="/sport/fussball/internationale-ligen/article68ece65a5e77548821fa1d0d/kylian-mbappe-er-hat-kein-leben-sagt-seine-mutter.html" title="„Er hat kein Leben. Das macht mich traurig“" data-external="Teaser.Link" data-internal-tracking-enabled="true" data-internal-tracking="{&quot;action&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;panorama_a_free&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Inline Element&quot;,&quot;data&quot;:{&quot;source&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;/sport/fussball/internationale-ligen/article68ece65a5e77548821fa1d0d/kylian-mbappe-er-hat-kein-leben-sagt-seine-mutter.html&quot;,&quot;trackingName&quot;:&quot;„Er hat kein Leben. Das macht mich traurig“&quot;,&quot;trackingLabel&quot;:&quot;„Er hat kein Leben. Das macht mich traurig“&quot;}}" aria-label="Internationale Ligen - Mbappés Mutter: „Er hat kein Leben. Das macht mich traurig“">„Er hat kein Leben. Das macht mich traurig“</a></h4><p class="c-teaser__intro" data-external="Teaser.Intro">Kylian Mbappé gehört zu den weltweit größten Fußballstars. Doch machen Reichtum und Ruhm wirklich glücklich? Abseits des Platzes offenbar nicht, wie seine besorgte Mutter verrät. Sie fürchte eine psychische Krise bei ihrem Sohn.</p></div><script type="application/hydration-data" data-internal-ref="TeaserFooter-613fc0bc-9220-40de-7f2a-980a6c1a5b54">{"teaserId":"68ece65a5e77548821fa1d0d","showCommentCount":true}</script><div data-component="TeaserFooter" data-internal-id="TeaserFooter-613fc0bc-9220-40de-7f2a-980a6c1a5b54" class="is-teaser-footer-hydrated"></div></div></article></div><div data-external="Stage.Item" class="u-grid-item is-grid-col-mobile-s-12 is-grid-col-mobile-l-6 is-grid-col-tablet-l-4"><article class="c-teaser c-teaser--default is-last" data-external="Teaser" data-external-id="68eb9a9e74c7beddb54e5dab"><div class="c-teaser__container"><header class="c-teaser__header" data-external="Teaser.Header"><div class="c-picture has-placeholder-image is-aspect-ratio-mobile-s-23x11  c-picture--default" data-external="Teaser.PictureElement.Placeholder"><picture class="c-picture__image-container is-aspect-ratio-mobile-s-23x11 "><source media="(min-width:0px)" srcSet="https://images.welt.de/68eb9a9e74c7beddb54e5dab/6a245e59462b38fef0bf01ef70add845/ci23x11-w200/canada-news-july-31-20