y und Kanadas Ex-Premier Justin Trudeau ein Paar sind.</p></div><script type="application/hydration-data" data-internal-ref="TeaserFooter-4b6f0313-2627-4b2c-8b69-eeb9d9d31e51">{"teaserId":"68eb9a9e74c7beddb54e5dab","showCommentCount":true}</script><div data-component="TeaserFooter" data-internal-id="TeaserFooter-4b6f0313-2627-4b2c-8b69-eeb9d9d31e51" class="is-teaser-footer-hydrated"></div></div></article></div></div></section><hr class="c-divider c-divider--stage"/><section class="c-ad-container" data-info-ad-placement="mrec_btf_5" aria-hidden="true"><script type="application/hydration-data" data-internal-ref="AdStage-c6830b6d-cb2b-4a98-7d89-e62544e761c1">{"adSlotProps":{"context":"stage","placementName":"mrec_btf_5","showAdLabel":true},"modifiers":"is-mrec is-mrec-btf-5 u-is-hidden-desktop"}</script><div data-component="AdStage" data-internal-id="AdStage-c6830b6d-cb2b-4a98-7d89-e62544e761c1"><div class="c-ad-stage is-mrec is-mrec-btf-5 u-is-hidden-desktop u-is-visibility-hidden"><div class="c-ad-slot c-ad-slot--stage"><span class="c-ad-slot__label">Anzeige</span><div class="c-ad-slot__placement" data-internal-ad="mrec_btf_5"><div id='mrec_btf_5'></div></div></div><hr class="c-divider c-divider--stage"/></div></div><script>
