="c-teaser__badge " data-external="Teaser.Badge"><a class="is-link c-teaser__badge-link is-teaser-link" href="/geschichte/" title="Geschichte" data-internal-tracking-enabled="true" data-internal-tracking="{&quot;action&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;link&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Inline Element&quot;,&quot;data&quot;:{&quot;source&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;/geschichte/&quot;,&quot;trackingName&quot;:&quot;Geschichte&quot;,&quot;trackingLabel&quot;:&quot;Geschichte&quot;}}" tabindex="-1"><span class="u-visually-hidden">Ressort<!-- -->:</span>Geschichte</a></span><span class="c-teaser__topic" data-external="Teaser.Topic">Lufthansa-Entführung 1977</span></div></div><div class="c-teaser__body" data-external="Teaser.Body"><h4 class="c-teaser__headline" data-external="Teaser.Title"><a class="is-link c-teaser__headline-link is-teaser-link" href="/geschichte/article68e391dc9501ad4ccbc03d9f/lufthansa-entfuehrung-1977-dieses-buch-leistet-was-der-mit-steuer-millionen-gepaeppelte-lernort-nicht-leisten-will.html" title="Dieses Buch leistet, was der mit Steuer-Millionen gepäppelte „Lernort“ nicht leisten will" data-external="Teaser.Link" data-internal-tracking-enabled="true" data-internal-tracking="{&quot;action&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;geschichte_a_free&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Inline Element&quot;,&quot;data&quot;:{&quot;source&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;/geschichte/article68e391dc9501ad4ccbc03d9f/lufthansa-entfuehrung-1977-dieses-buch-leistet-was-der-mit-steuer-millionen-gepaeppelte-lernort-nicht-leisten-will.html&quot;,&quot;trackingName&quot;:&quot;Dieses Buch leistet, was der mit Steuer-Millionen gepäppelte „Lernort“ nicht leisten will&quot;,&quot;trackingLabel&quot;:&quot;Dieses Buch leistet, was der mit Steuer-Millionen gepäppelte „Lernort“ nicht leisten will&quot;}}" aria-label="Geschichte - Lufthansa-Entführung 1977: Dieses Buch leistet, was der mit Steuer-Millionen gepäppelte „Lernort“ nicht leisten will">Dieses Buch leistet, was der mit Steuer-Millionen gepäppelte „Lernort“ nicht leisten will</a></h4><p class="c-teaser__intro" data-external="Teaser.Intro">Mit Millionenaufwand wird ein „Lernort ‚Landshut‘“ in Friedrichshafen errichtet. Doch das Projekt geht am Publikum vorbei. Wer wirklich wissen will, was sich im „Deutschen Herbst“ abgespielt hat, muss das neue Buch von Martin Rupps lesen.</p></div><script type="application/hydration-data" data-internal-ref="TeaserFooter-ae07842f-b708-47e0-7b4a-dc77840c92ac">{"teaserId":"68e391dc9501ad4ccbc03d9f","showCommentCount":true,"author":{"name":"Sven-Felix Kellerhoff"}}</script><div data-component="TeaserFooter" data-internal-id="TeaserFooter-ae07842f-b708-47e0-7b4a-dc77840c92ac" class="is-teaser-footer-hydrated"><footer class="c-teaser__footer" data-external="Teaser.Footer"><ul class="c-teaser__footer-list"><li class="c-teaser__footer-list-item"><span class="c-teaser__author" data-external="Teaser.Author">Sven-Felix Kellerhoff</span></li></ul></footer></div></div></article></div><div data-external="Stage.Item" class="u-grid-item is-grid-col-mobile-s-12 is-grid-col-mobile-l-6 is-grid-col-tablet-l-4"><article class="c-teaser c-teaser--default is-last" data-external="Teaser" data-external-id="68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f"><div class="c-teaser__container"><header class="c-teaser__header" data-external="Teaser.Header"><div class="c-picture has-placeholder-image is-aspect-ratio-mobile-s-23x11  c-picture--default" data-external="Teaser.PictureElement.Placeholder"><picture class="c-picture__image-container is-aspect-ratio-mobile-s-23x11 "><source media="(min-width:0px)" srcSet="https://images.welt.de/68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f/9c2264cb92059855f164a64ac614a46c/ci23x11-w200/the-cole-bombing 200w, https://images.welt.de/68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f/9c2264cb92059855f164a64ac614a46c/ci23x11-w400/the-cole-bombing 400w, https://images.welt.de/68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f/9c2264cb92059855f164a64ac614a46c/ci23x11-w600/the-cole-bombing 600w, https://images.welt.de/68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f/9c2264cb92059855f164a64ac614a46c/ci23x11-w800/the-cole-bombing 800w, https://images.welt.de/68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f/9c2264cb92059855f164a64ac614a46c/ci23x11-w1000/the-cole-bombing 1000w, https://images.welt.de/68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f/9c2264cb92059855f164a64ac614a46c/ci23x11-w1200/the-cole-bombing 1200w, https://images.welt.de/68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f/9c2264cb92059855f164a64ac614a46c/ci23x11-w1400/the-cole-bombing 1400w, https://images.welt.de/68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f/9c2264cb92059855f164a64ac614a46c/ci23x11-w1600/the-cole-bombing 1600w, https://images.welt.de/68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f/9c2264cb92059855f164a64ac614a46c/ci23x11-w1800/the-cole-bombing 1800w, https://images.welt.de/68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f/9c2264cb92059855f164a64ac614a46c/ci23x11-w2000/the-cole-bombing 2000w" sizes="(min-width: 910px) calc(970px / 3), (min-width: 600px) 50vw, 100vw"/><img src="https://images.welt.de/68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f/9c2264cb92059855f164a64ac614a46c/ci23x11-w200/the-cole-bombing" class="c-picture__image" alt="383987 09: U.S. Navy and Marine Corps security personnel patrol past the damaged U.S. Navy destroyer USS Cole (DDG 67) following the October 12, 2000 terrorist bombing attack on the ship in Aden, Yemen, October 18, 2000. Security personnel established checkpoints and searched incoming vehicles for contraband and explosives while the ship was prepared for its journey back to the United States. (Photo by Lyle G. Becker/U.S. Navy/Newsmakers) Getty ImagesGetty Images" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></picture></div></header></div><div class="c-teaser__container is-full-height-flex"><div class="c-teaser__overline"><div class="c-teaser__ellipsis-container"><span class="c-teaser__badge " data-external="Teaser.Badge"><a class="is-link c-teaser__badge-link is-teaser-link" href="/geschichte/" title="Geschichte" data-internal-tracking-enabled="true" data-internal-tracking="{&quot;action&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;link&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Inline Element&quot;,&quot;data&quot;:{&quot;source&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;/geschichte/&quot;,&quot;trackingName&quot;:&quot;Geschichte&quot;,&quot;trackingLabel&quot;:&quot;Geschichte&quot;}}" tabindex="-1"><span class="u-visually-hidden">Ressort<!-- -->:</span>Geschichte</a></span><span class="c-teaser__topic" data-external="Teaser.Topic">Anschlag auf USS „Cole“</span></div></div><div class="c-teaser__body" data-external="Teaser.Body"><h4 class="c-teaser__headline" data-external="Teaser.Title"><a class="is-link c-teaser__headline-link is-teaser-link" href="/geschichte/article68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f/anschlag-auf-uss-cole-der-tod-kam-per-muellboot.html" title="Der Tod kam per Müllboot" data-external="Teaser.Link" data-internal-tracking-enabled="true" data-internal-tracking="{&quot;action&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;geschichte_a_free&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Inline Element&quot;,&quot;data&quot;:{&quot;source&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;/geschichte/article68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f/anschlag-auf-uss-cole-der-tod-kam-per-muellboot.html&quot;,&quot;trackingName&quot;:&quot;Der Tod kam per Müllboot&quot;,&quot;trackingLabel&quot;:&quot;Der Tod kam per Müllboot&quot;}}" aria-label="Geschichte - Anschlag auf USS „Cole“: Der Tod kam per Müllboot">Der Tod kam per Müllboot</a></h4><p class="c-teaser__intro" data-external="Teaser.Intro">Der Zerstörer USS „Cole“ tankte am 12. Oktober 2000 im Hafen von Aden auf, als eine gewaltige Explosion ein Loch in den Rumpf riss. 17 Mitglieder der Besatzung starben. Verantwortlich war eine Al-Qaida-Zelle im Jemen.</p></div><script type="application/hydration-data" data-internal-ref="TeaserFooter-354bb572-7f68-4f14-7de1-40e3755a2005">{"teaserId":"68dd1aa3381f1ea56f35922f","showCommentCount":true,"author":{"name":"Johann Althaus"}}</script><div data-component="TeaserFooter" data-internal-id="TeaserFooter-354bb572-7f68-4f14-7de1-40e3755a2005" class